72. Write the PHP program to implement the following session functions.
(i)session_register() (ii) session_unset() (iii) session_destroy()
<?php
session_start();
// (i) session_register() is deprecated; instead, directly use $_SESSION
$_SESSION['username'] = "Kavya";
// Display session value
echo "Username: " . $_SESSION['username'] . "<br>";
// (ii) Unset a session variable
session_unset(); // removes all session variables
echo "Session unset!<br>";
// (iii) Destroy the session
session_destroy();
echo "Session destroyed!";
?>
